b85","tid":1453234,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港需要人道救援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當下，香港極需要不受滋擾的中立醫療團隊。我們需要無國界醫生、聯合國維和部隊，以及其他人道救援組織。只有他們可以為香港提供正常醫療保障，免於中共香港警察滋擾。以下這個聯署，是要求美國派遣醫療船以提供中立的醫療服務。美國醫療船扺達後，其他國際醫療組織就更易來港協助，以減低香港人在今次戰爭的傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n這是十分實際的要求，也是極為急切和重要。為免香港發生大規模人道災難，請各位簽署並廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=3c34606e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster</a>"},{"pid":"395390f242c8a0bf1da2139d13f2a51ee1386989","tid":1453234,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"嘩 好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bffd1d739a6f8fab7a35e210512a30f3dcb2783","tid":1453234,"uid":294984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"夠撚薑就喺機場開戰"},{"pid":"0a95017b03c6d3028723aa0cfb7dde31052eb803","tid":1453234,"uid":77202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"佐敦一向都有<br />\n大驚小怪"},{"pid":"95bd90af95ebc4aa56ee04588d380da23f566ec8","tid":1453234,"uid":6142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"殺我囉，我爛命一條"},{"pid":"937e8e2f47f96fc17d53c7ab7e23e4f6f4d067bd","tid":1453234,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"夠薑咪機場出囉"},{"pid":"5bca8249a0038d3c77262ff108dc7285f4c9fca7","tid":1453234,"uid":73694,"like":0,"di